00:06:21.255 --> 00:06:23.235
Common mistakes and misconceptions.

00:06:23.595 --> 00:06:25.635
Let's clear up some common confusion.

00:06:25.995 --> 00:06:30.015
A big mistake is believing
KYC is only for new customers.

00:06:30.285 --> 00:06:34.845
The correction is that KYC is an
ongoing process and even existing

00:06:34.845 --> 00:06:36.765
customers need periodic updates.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:40.520
A common misconception is
that any ID card will work.

00:06:40.789 --> 00:06:44.090
The correction is that only
specific officially valid

00:06:44.090 --> 00:06:46.340
documents or ovd are accepted.

00:06:46.700 --> 00:06:50.870
Another mistake is thinking KYC
is just about collecting papers.

00:06:51.020 --> 00:06:55.580
No, the correction is that it involves
understanding the customer's financial

00:06:55.580 --> 00:06:56.955
behavior and source of funds.

00:06:57.719 --> 00:07:01.469
A misconception is that low risk
customers need zero monitoring.

00:07:01.620 --> 00:07:02.430
Wrong again.

00:07:02.700 --> 00:07:07.590
They still require basic monitoring to
spot any changes, and a final mistake

00:07:07.650 --> 00:07:10.049
is ignoring small problems in documents.

00:07:10.260 --> 00:07:15.030
The correction is that any discrepancy
must be investigated and fixed, or

00:07:15.030 --> 00:07:16.650
the bank could be in big trouble.

